        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nthanks doc is nice\nhttps://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/rtdv3-global-verify-master/2614/docs/docs_5G_PNF_Software_Upgrade_With_Schema_Update.html\n\nThe test description remains relatively generic, is there any simple test procedure to be highlighted to verify this new feature on any ONAP - typically a service package + its \"possible upgrade\" hellow world files.\nultimately it would be nice to create an automatic case based on these files to cover this new SO feature in gate (and be sure there will be no regression in the future).\nIf you have already a test procedure somewhere..\nwe can easily onboard a service using the pythonsdk, add artifacts such as tca blueprint and call the so even if I do not think thta this part of the API is covered in the python onapsdk (https://gitlab.com/Orange-OpenSource/lfn/onap/python-onapsdk/-/tree/develop/src/onapsdk/so) but it could be added..",
